=== Noun ===
'''sheep''' (''plural'': sheep)

#a [[woolly]] [[ruminant]] of the genus ''[[Ovis]]''. Male: [[ram]] (intact), [[weether]] (castrated). Female: [[ewe]].  Young: [[lamb]]. Carnal: [[lamb]], [[mutton]].
#a timid, shy person who is easily led by others.

